<br>
If a situation comes up like the one Caeona had, and the whole group agrees to let the last winner roll (maybe it was for something not too useful to most people, like a CHA augment or something,) then, groovy, go ahead and roll.  But one person should not come away with 5 new things while everyone else gets nothing.  If an item upgrades only one person's gear, i.e. a monk only drop, or a knight only drop, it should go to them and them only.  Karma and reputations mean everything on FV.  Most decent folks here will not take an item that they have no use for, if another character can and will use it.  <br>
<br>
There's no &quot;set of rules,&quot; but there's basic inter-player courtesy.  Like not gating away from your group without a word.  This is just one of the things that players have to develop a code of honor for on their own, and I think 90% of the people on FV adhere to this system.  Or I just know all the decent folks. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=leapflycrashdie>LeapflyCrashdie</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 7<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(9/25/03 3:59 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4089.topic&index=29>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Shadowglade the Cleric (AKA Shadowgate)</span><hr size=1> Oops my bad sorry Shabba it was Asong... was tired when I posted and wasnt thinking right <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=echtelionfv>EchtelionFV</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 681<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(9/25/03 4:32 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4089.topic&index=30>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.hi-logic.com/Echtelion_avatar.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Shadowglade the Cleric (AKA Shadowgate)</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></stro