<br>
Projection is when you place atributes about <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>yourself</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> onto someone else, and generally, atributes you aren't comfortable dealing with. I suppose one could project things onto a person that had nothing to do with themselves, but that is generally called sterotyping. Like saying, fat people can't control thier eating when your a skinny person.<br>
<br>
In this case, I'm addressing a persons actions, not what I <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>assume</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> about them. His <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>action</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> was to make someone prove he wasn't lying about what items he had in an attempt to get a chance to make a claim on the item.<br>
<br>
That is the difference. Someone can ask to roll on everysingle item. Are they a loot whore, does that mean they try and cheat people? No. The difference here is the actions he took after the other 4 people said they didn't mind it going to the monk. What someone actually does can be judged. Just as you are judging what I posted. <br>
<br>
Considering that someone would try and prove deception on someone else part, simply out of the the desire to gain more for themselves, against the voice of the rest of the group says to me they are willing to practice tricks and deception <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>themselves</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END-->.<br>
<br>
If someone is willing to decive, for personal gain, it's perfectly right for me to think that this is how they behave. If you think that is projection, go right ahead. But then, wouldn't that be the same thing you are doing? Projecting that I project onto people? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=oliiasmoorglade>OliiasMoorglade</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 681<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(9/25/03 9:02 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4089.topic&index=37>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.thephosphorbox.com/cptrply-small.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Shadowglade the Cleric (AKA Shadowgate)</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>Only someone obsessed with loot would think everyone ELSE was greedy too<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
